data.description: Welcome Home! Located in Terracita, this beautifully remodeled  residence is a perfect blend of modern comfort and timeless elegance. Newer HVAC, fresh paint inside and out, new Blinds, gorgeous granite counter tops, upgraded laminate flooring and so much more. This stunning home offers 4 beds, 2.5 baths, & a 2-car garage. Discover formal living & family rooms graced with layered crown molding, wood-look laminate plank flooring, recessed lighting, and abundant natural light. The eat-in kitchen boasts SS appliances, a walk-in pantry, an island, and ample white cabinetry. Head upstairs to find a versatile loft, ideal for a play/TV area! Also including the bedrooms, each having carpet & a walk-in closet. Large main bedroom stands out with a double-door entry & a spotless bathroom. Venture into the spacious backyard, your private retreat! The covered patio is for relaxing, while lush grass provides room for lively gatherings. Seller is willing to help with interest rate buy down option with a full price offer. Don't miss out on this opportunity, schedule your private tour Now!!
